-costa-luminosa3\">{{cite web |url=https://www.costacruises.com/fleet/luminosa/v1.html |title=Costa Luminosa |work=CostaCruises.com |date= |access-date=20 March 2020}}</ref> (a subsidiary of [[Carnival Corporation & plc|Carnival Corporation]])<ref name=\"ship-costa-luminosa\" />\n| \n| 3\n| 1\n|-\n\n| {{ship||Ruby Princess}}\n| ~2,700<ref name=\"ship-ruby-princess\">{{cite web |url=https://www.businessinsider.com/passengers-ruby-princess-cruise-sydney-positive-for-coronavirus-2020-3 |title=Officials are scrambling to round up 3,800 passengers and staff who disembarked from the Ruby Princess cruise in Sydney after 4 people tested positive for coronavirus |work=Business Insider |date= |access-date=20 March 2020}}</ref>\n| 1,100<ref name=\"ship-ruby-princess\" />\n| \n| 19 March 2020<ref name=\"ship-ruby-princess\" />\n| [[Sydney Harbor]], [[Sydney, Australia]]<ref name=\"ship-ruby-princess\" />\n| [[Princess Cruises]]<ref name=\"ship-ruby-princess2\">{{cite web |url=https://www.princess.com/ships-and-experience/ships/ru-ruby-princess/ |title=Ruby Princess Cruise Ship |work=Princess.com |date= |access-date=20 March 2020}}</ref> (a subsidiary of [[Carnival Corporation & plc|Carnival Corporation]])\n| \n| 440<ref name=\"guardian2020-03-31\"/>\n| 5<ref name=\"seven2020-03-31\"/>\n|-\n\n| {{ship||Celebrity Solstice}}<ref name=\"ship-voyager-of-the-seas\" />\n| \n| \n| \n| 20 March 2020<ref name=\"ship-voyager-of-the-seas\" />\n| [[Sydney Harbor]], [[Sydney, Australia]]<ref name=\"ship-voyager-of-the-seas\" />\n| [[Celebrity Cruises]]<ref name=\"cruise-owner-celebrity-cruises\">{{cite web |url=https://www.celebritycruises.com/cruise-ships/celebrity-solstice |title=Solstice|work=Celebrity Cruises |date= |access-date=23 March 2020}}</ref>  \n| \n| \n| \n|-\n| {{ship||Costa Magica}}<ref name=ThreeSmall/>\n| 2,309<ref name=\"ship-costa-magica\">{{cite web |url=https://www.urdupoint.com/en/world/virus-affected-costa-magica-cruise-ship-in-ca-863815.html |title=Virus-Affected Cost